articles.title: AUB targets P4 billion net income in 2021 - BusinessWorld Online
articles.description: ASIA UNITED Bank Corp. (AUB) targets to grow its net profit by 30% to P4 billion this year on hopes that improving consumer confidence will boost its lending business, it said in a statement on Friday.  AUB’s net income dropped 38% to P736 million in the firs…

articles.title: Japan to donate 1 million AstraZeneca shots to Asian nations - New Straits Times
articles.description: ANKARA: Japan on Friday announced it will provide Oxford-AstraZeneca’s Covid-19 vaccines to Asian nations starting next week, according to Anadolu.
